co" alt="James Trimarco" /></a><div class="media-body"><h5 class="media-heading"><a href="http://www.yesmagazine.org/@@also-by?author=James+Trimarco">James Trimarco</a></h5><a class="pull-left" href="http://www.yesmagazine.org/issues/50-solutions/where-citizens-can-run-for-office-without-big-money-and-win-20161104">Where Citizens Can Run for Office Without Big Money—and Win</a></div></div><div class="media"><a class="pull-left" href="http://www.yesmagazine.org/@@also-by?author=Zenobia+Jeffries"><img class="media-object" src="http://www.yesmagazine.org/portal_memberdata/portraits/zjeffries" alt="Zenobia Jeffries" /></a><div class="media-body"><h5 class="media-heading"><a href="http://www.yesmagazine.org/@@also-by?author=Zenobia+Jeffries">Zenobia Jeffries</a></h5><a class="pull-left" href="http://www.yesmagazine.org/peace-justice/the-call-to-end-the-war-on-black-lives-starts-with-accountability-20161103">The Call to “End the War on Black Lives” Starts With Accountability</a></div></div><div class="media"><a class="pull-left" href=""><img class="media-object" src="" alt="" /></a><div class="media-body"><h5 class="media-heading"><a href=""></a></h5><a class="pull-left" href=""></a></div></div></div><!-- /#voices-rows -->
